iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDksOhi9C6sCDkNp6u_1DoxueWd32HjvX2ZWMdjFubphA&oe=67712B9D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "ang taggers.png", "id": "1735060820635299", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031520_1735060823968632_4194688242813973977_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mZI63V-z3ioQ7kNvgGxtFIo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCa7korfqUbC7YoOwB4RJCKAHXTYQfaFPd56FI0Abmq9g&oe=67713973"}, "display_name": "ANG TAGGERS", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Immerse yourself in the wild, fast-paced world of Ang Taggers, where agility, strategy, and reflexes are key to survival. In this exhilarating multiplayer experience, you and your friends become dynamic creatures navigating a sprawling jungle landscape filled with towering trees, treacherous cliffs, and hidden caverns.\n\nAs an Ang Tagger, you\u2019ll engage in heart-pounding chases, scaling natural obstacles with your unparalleled climbing skills. Every match brings a new challenge, with varied environments and weather conditions that demand quick thinking and adaptability. The intuitive movement mechanics allow you to leap, swing, and vault with ease, making every escape and capture a thrilling experience.\n\nCustomize your character with a variety of skins and accessories, and earn rewards through daring feats and clever tactics. Team up or go solo in different game modes, each offering unique objectives and excitement. Whether you're evading capture or closing in on your target, Ang Taggers promises endless fun and adrenaline-fueled action.\n\nJoin the vibrant community of players, compete in seasonal events, and climb the leaderboards to prove you're the ultimate Ang Tagger. Are you ready to embrace the chase and dominate the jungle?\n", "short_description": "A fun tagging game where you are a monkey and tag other monkeys."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/vie